{
  "shellOpenBeforeHeader": "\n\n<div class=\"lp-root font-sans antialiased\">\n\n  \n  ",
  "pageContentBetweenShell": "\n  <div class=\"h-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-(--beige-light)\">\n    <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-360 px-6 sm:px-14 lg:px-24 pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-14 sm:pb-20\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center\">\n        <p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.35em] uppercase mb-6\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">Áreas de Práctica</p>\n        <h1 class=\"font-serif italic font-semibold leading-[1.1] text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-8\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Asesoría integral en cada<br>disciplina del derecho</h1>\n        <p class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Cada materia jurídica exige un enfoque propio. Nuestro equipo combina rigor técnico y trato cercano para proteger sus intereses en todas las ramas del derecho, con estrategias diseñadas a la medida de su caso.</p>\n        <div class=\"mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n          <span class=\"h-px w-16\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></span>\n          <span class=\"text-lg\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">§</span>\n          <span class=\"h-px w-16\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-(--beige-main)\">\n    <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-360 px-6 sm:px-14 lg:px-24 py-16 sm:py-24\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-end justify-between mb-12 flex-wrap gap-4\">\n        <h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl\" style=\"color:var(--charcoal)\">Nueve áreas de especialización</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-sm max-w-xs\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Explore las disciplinas en las que ofrecemos representación y consejo experto.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"columns-1 md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-6\">\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-scale-balanced text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Penal</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Defensa penal estratégica y representación en litigios ante los tribunales de justicia.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5);background:linear-gradient(160deg,#fff,var(--beige-light))\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-6\">\n            <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\">\n              <i class=\"fa-solid fa-graduation-cap text-3xl\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full\" style=\"background:var(--beige-main);color:var(--copper)\">Especialidad</span>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Educacional</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Asesoría en normativa escolar, procedimientos y conflictos educativos, con acompañamiento a toda la comunidad.</p>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n            <span class=\"text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border\" style=\"border-color:var(--rose-main);color:var(--rose-dark)\">Apoderados</span>\n            <span class=\"text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border\" style=\"border-color:var(--rose-main);color:var(--rose-dark)\">Docentes</span>\n            <span class=\"text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border\" style=\"border-color:var(--rose-main);color:var(--rose-dark)\">Sostenedores</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-file-contract text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Civil</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Contratos, responsabilidad civil y cumplimiento de obligaciones patrimoniales.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 rounded-lg p-8 border-0 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"background:var(--rose-dark);color:var(--beige-light)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--rose-light)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-house-chimney text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--rose-light)\">Área Destacada</p>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-3 text-white\">Decreto Ley 2.695</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5\" style=\"color:var(--beige-main)\">Regularización de la pequeña propiedad raíz y saneamiento de títulos de dominio de bienes nacionales, un procedimiento técnico que dominamos con experiencia.</p>\n          <span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium\" style=\"color:var(--rose-light)\">Bienes Nacionales\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long text-xs\"></i>\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <a href=\"derecho-familia.html\" class=\"svc block break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-people-roof text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Familia</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Divorcios, pensiones de alimentos y regímenes de cuidado personal.</p>\n        </a>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-briefcase text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Laboral</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Despidos, negociación colectiva y defensa de derechos laborales.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-building text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Inmobiliaria</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Compraventa, arriendos y litigios inmobiliarios de todo tipo.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-plane-departure text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Aeronáutico</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Derecho aeronáutico y cumplimiento de la normativa de la DGAC.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"svc break-inside-avoid mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border transition-all duration-300\" style=\"border-color:rgba(166,138,109,.5)\">\n          <div style=\"color:var(--copper)\" class=\"mb-6\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-landmark text-3xl\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Administrativo</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Procedimientos y recursos ante la administración del Estado.</p>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-(--beige-light)\">\n   <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-360 px-6 sm:px-14 lg:px-24 py-16 sm:py-24\">\n    <p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-center\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">Nuestro Método</p>\n    <h2 class=\"font-serif italic text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center mb-16\" style=\"color:var(--rose-dark)\">Un proceso claro en cada caso</h2>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-x-10 gap-y-12\">\n      <div class=\"proc-step px-1\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl leading-none\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">01</span>\n        <div class=\"h-px w-full my-6\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-serif text-xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--charcoal)\">Consulta inicial</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Escuchamos su situación y evaluamos con claridad las alternativas legales disponibles.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proc-step px-1\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl leading-none\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">02</span>\n        <div class=\"h-px w-full my-6\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-serif text-xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--charcoal)\">Análisis del caso</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Estudiamos los antecedentes en profundidad y determinamos la viabilidad jurídica.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proc-step px-1\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl leading-none\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">03</span>\n        <div class=\"h-px w-full my-6\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-serif text-xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--charcoal)\">Estrategia</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Diseñamos un plan de acción a la medida de sus objetivos y prioridades.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proc-step px-1\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-6xl leading-none\" style=\"color:var(--copper)\">04</span>\n        <div class=\"h-px w-full my-6\" style=\"background:var(--beige-dark)\"></div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-serif text-xl mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--charcoal)\">Representación</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--gray-text)\">Le acompañamos y defendemos con firmeza hasta la resolución definitiva.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n\n\n  <section class=\"bg-(--rose-dark)\">\n   <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-360 px-6 sm:px-14 lg:px-24 py-16 sm:py-24\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\">\n      <span class=\"text-3xl\" style=\"color:var(--rose-light)\">§</span>\n      <h2 class=\"font-serif italic text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mt-4 mb-5\">¿No encuentra su área?</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-lg mb-10\" style=\"color:var(--rose-light)\">Consulte con nosotros. Evaluamos cada caso de forma personalizada y le orientamos sin compromiso hacia la mejor solución jurídica.</p>\n      <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center\">\n        <a href=\"contact.html\" class=\"btn-fill px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-medium\" style=\"background:var(--beige-light);color:var(--rose-dark)\">Solicitar consulta</a>\n        <a href=\"https://wa.me/56987654321\" class=\"btn-fill px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-medium text-white border flex items-center gap-2\" style=\"border-color:var(--rose-light)\">\n          <i class=\"fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-lg\"></i>\n          WhatsApp\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n\n  ",
